            "notes": "The main idea of this control deck is to manipulate the game by countering opponent's spells, disrupting their strategy, and generating card advantage through Tasigur's abilities. The deck includes a wide range of counterspells, removal spells, card draw, and tutors to control the pace of the game. With a mix of permission spells, removal, and card advantage engines, the deck aims to grind out opponents by out-valuing them in the long game. Tasigur's ability to recur cards from the graveyard provides additional value and allows for flexibility in adapting to different game situations. Overall, the key strategy is to outlast opponents, disrupt their plans, and slowly build up incremental advantages to secure a victory."
